{"tid":1618231,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【每日幾秒】TVB連累廣告商，每日洗版任務 - 恒生銀行","createTime":"2019-10-04T04:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:16:19.000Z","uid":267969,"like":56,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1a09b29e0083a06185f1801ea83396823fa6657d","tid":1618231,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各位marketing JJ注意，<br />\nTVB係品牌負資產，喺TVB落廣告，你哋苦心經營嘅品牌形象將付諸流水！無人可憐！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">今個月</span></span>開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">年底</span></span>啦！<br />\n廣告界多番強調，去FB洗版係有用ga</strong><br />\n <br />\n恒生成日標榜自己係服務香港人既銀行，但佢屢屢出賣港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n早年取消註冊民運社團戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、近年封殺周庭收捐款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、而家仲要喺CCTVB賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n各位恒生用戶，係時候㩒錢換美金啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCash is King!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/71656384_465449974311857_8590002881980006400_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQnit0kKc0BHdqo_UDjsLubJ42bkOx9iee_JUFpgA7hmP_H2_WOL9LhOgjChJi3RnlM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=61b100ca0b903b987bf0730db20b968d&amp;oe=5E315B57\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F71656384_465449974311857_8590002881980006400_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQnit0kKc0BHdqo_UDjsLubJ42bkOx9iee_JUFpgA7hmP_H2_WOL9LhOgjChJi3RnlM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D61b100ca0b903b987bf0730db20b968d%26oe%3D5E315B57&h=f9e65439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   --&gt; 洗版話㩒錢 + 剪卡<br />\n <br />\n是日精選@4 Oct 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>恒生銀行</strong></span></span> <strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HangSengInvestment\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHangSengInvestment&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3hjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=0a345fcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HangSengInvestment</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hangsengchatbot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhangsengchatbot&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3hjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=30b664a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hangsengchatbot</a></span></strong> <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請用幾秒</span></strong>去派嬲、留言、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得?</span></strong>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />P牌只開行動post，順便follow埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">※請善用template，清晰表達訴求</span></span><br />\n二擇其一，歡迎創意留言。</strong> <br />\n1️⃣<br />\n無綫新聞，助紂為虐，恥與為伍，撤回廣告！記唔記得4年前嘅梁烈唯剪卡運動呢？唔好低估香港人嘅決心，請立即撤回TVB廣告。希望貴公司重新檢視你所僱用之廣告公司及其廣告計劃。貴公司有權選擇其他廣告公司，正如大眾同樣有權選擇你的競爭對手！<br />\n2️⃣<br />\n我本身好支持你哋公司嘅產品，奈何本人對貴公司於賣港媒體TVB落廣告此舉極為反感，決定罷買產品直至見唔到TVB 廣告為止。<span style=\"color: red;\">記唔記得4年前嘅梁烈唯剪卡運動呢？唔好低估香港人嘅決心，請立即撤回TVB廣告</span>。如果廣告部或者廣告公司hard sell 你買TVB，請考慮換咗廣告部同事或廣告公司！<br />\n <br />\n歡迎大家用呢幅圖留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BQyNN72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBQyNN72.jpg&h=11632ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span>: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span> <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3hjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=ad01e392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a>  <br />\n －－－－－－－ <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3hjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=ded8865d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb[/quote]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb%5B%2Fquote%5D&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3hjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=ad171680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb[/quote]</a>"},{"pid":"7217bac3f1797c722ffd3888679dcb650cf0e0db","tid":1618231,"uid":265902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:58:45.000Z","msg":"P牌幫推"},{"pid":"7e7c1014aa5a1f452a8cdd04e5ba229c9614011b","tid":1618231,"uid":262379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T04:58:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3fe3d5ad45348dde79fea6776d8985987ead777","tid":1618231,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:00:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7f54b498adef18f8a6834fef60b4e36939081bc","tid":1618231,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike